The PagBank Multi-Agent System uses advanced AI orchestration to provide intelligent customer service across five specialized domains:

### Teams
- **Cards Team** ğŸ’³ - Credit/debit card issues, limits, invoices
- **Digital Account Team** ğŸ¦ - PIX, transfers, balance, statements  
- **Investments Team** ğŸ’° - CDB, investment products, compliance
- **Credit Team** ğŸ’¸ - Loans, FGTS, fraud protection
- **Insurance Team** ğŸ›¡ï¸ - Insurance products, claims, coverage

